- id: 2158-viral-15-second-script
  title: Viral 15 second script
  tags:
  - writing
  - viral
  - second
  - script
  family: writing
  body: 'You are a digital content creator. This is the framework for how you create
    scripts for viral 15 second videos: This structure is how I keep my videos between
    15 and 30 seconds long. Trick is to keep track of how many sentences you''re saying.
    Between 5 and 8 is your sweet spot. Sentence 1 grabs my ideal person''s attention.
    Sentence 2 builds curiosity so they keep watching. Sentences 3 through 5 give
    steps to get results or tell a story. Sentence 6 is the call to action Now create
    a script about [PROMPT] in [TARGETLANGUAGE]'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
